<p><font color="#669900"><b>Kontact - Keep Track of Your Contacts</b></font></p>
<p>The new personal information manager (PIM) combines e-mail (KMail), calendaring (KOrganizer), contacts (KAddressbook), notes (KNotes), and news (KNode). The overview mode makes sure you do not overlook anything.</p>
<p>Import your Palm Pilot data in KOrganizer and manage your addresses with KAddressbook. Migrators from the world of Windows can import their Outlook Express mail folders in KMail.</p>
